dcterms:description: A set of continuous control tasks that simulate scenarios encountered by robots in real life, including Hopper-v2, HalfCheetah-v2, and Walker2d-v2. The tasks involve selecting the amount of torque to apply to each joint of the robot.
dcterms:title: Mujoco tasks (Hopper-v2, HalfCheetah-v2, Walker2d-v2)

dcterms:creator: H. Le
C. Voloshin
Y. Yue
dcterms:description: A dataset used for learning safe policies by applying Fitted Q Evaluation (FQE) and Fitted Q Iteration (FQI). It is designed for constrained batch policy learning.
dcterms:title: CBPL (Constrained Batch Policy Learning)

dcterms:creator: S. Fujimoto
D. Meger
D. Precup
dcterms:description: A dataset used for off-policy deep reinforcement learning without exploration, focusing on learning from previously collected data.
dcterms:title: BCQ (Behavioral Cloning with Q-learning)

dcterms:creator: A. Kumar
A. Zhou
G. Tucker
S. Levine
dcterms:description: A dataset used for conservative Q-learning in offline reinforcement learning, focusing on learning from a fixed dataset without further exploration.
dcterms:title: BEAR (Behavioral Cloning with Q-learning)

dcterms:description: A dataset used for constrained policy optimization, focusing on learning policies that satisfy safety constraints.
